welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Narangba, a charming city known for its stunning natural beauty and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer, and we hope you enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Redcliffe Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The International Terminal at Brisbane Airport serves as the gateway to Australia for international travelers.

terminals.name: Domestic Terminal
terminals.description: The Domestic Terminal at Brisbane Airport is the busiest terminal, serving both domestic and regional flights within Australia.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Caloundra Airport serves domestic flights within Australia.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Caloundra Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the terminal for passengers to use.
